<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bang-v">bang <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bæŋ/    美 /bæŋ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>砰地关上：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He banged the window shut. 
他砰的一声关上了窗户。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>猛敲；猛撞：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>bang at / on a door 
砰砰敲门</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She walked so far back that she <strong>banged into</strong> another painting on the wall. 
她向后退得很远，撞到墙上的另一张画作上。</p><footer>译林③ – 1</footer></div></div>